Mizuno et al. (2006) implemented both Koide’s and Noble’s et al. 2D methods for primitive variable recovery in RAISHIN. The ECHO code incorporates the 2D, 1DW, 1Dυ2 and \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
