The specific initial conditions considered by Del Zanna et al. (2003) were ρ0 = 1, p0 = 0.1, A = 0. 01, and λ= 1. They performed simulations in 1D with (ξ, η, ζ) = (x, y,z) and B0 = 1, and in 2D with \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
