Giacomazzo and Rezzolla (2006) solved for the jump conditions considering By and Bz as the unknown quantities. In a first step, using Eqs. (4.13), (4.19), (4.20), and the shock invariant \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
